      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for your weekend getaways or daily commutes! It\u2019s been well-cared for and is totally ready to hit the road with someone new. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
