    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At the heart is the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, both recently serviced to ensure optimal valve timing and throttle response. The power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, a critical preventative measure for this platform. Suspension components remain tight, utilizing factory-spec dampers and bushings for a balanced longitudinal and lateral load distribution. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited driving, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain top-tier for the enthusiast seeking a driver-focused machine.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
