    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been driven with care. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium upholstery that remains firm and supportive, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the navigation system. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection completed just 1,500 miles ago. The tires offer ample tread for several more seasons, and the engine pulls cleanly without any hesitation or unusual noises. This is a reliable, honest vehicle ready for its next owner. Full service records and a clean title are available for review.",
